    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for reliable transportation on a budget. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dents, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and a small tear on the driver's seat, though all essential electronics and controls remain functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely need some suspension work and a tune-up in the near future to keep it at its best.",
      "price": 22500.0,
