      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary motorcar, preserved in a state of absolute refinement. This vehicle has been curated to meet the most rigorous standards of automotive excellence, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and a pristine interior environment that remains indistinguishable from its original showroom delivery. Every mechanical component has been subjected to exhaustive verification, ensuring performance that is both seamless and authoritative. This is a rare opportunity to secure a superlative specimen that caters to the requirements of the most discerning collector or enthusiast.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
